        "cooked": "<p>I’m afraid, I cant’t help with the issue itself, but there might be an option for you to roll back in the meantime.</p>\n<p>If you feel up to it, you could build an older version yourself and then uninstall the current one and replace it. Of course, this can cause issues as well, but if the current one seems unusable, that could be a good option.</p>",
